some insights from the correlation test

  1. The population of people in a country is weekly correlated to the total death recorded
  2. There was a strong correlation between total cases and total recovered
  3. There was astrong correlation between total cases and total deaths
  4. There was a weak correlation between tOtal cases and the population of the country affected
